{{! Verdict-line partial — Phase 57.
    The primary unit of evidence display per DESIGN.md.
    One sentence in display weight, plus a meta line with provenance.
    No icon. No badge. Type carries the weight.

    Inputs:
      sentence (string, required) — the verdict in plain language.
      meta     (string, required) — provenance line (date · standard · counts).
      status   (string, optional) — "pass"|"warn"|"fail"|"info" for status word colouring.
      statusLabel (string, optional) — short uppercase eyebrow above the sentence. }}

<header class="verdict-line" role="region" aria-label="Verdict">
  {{#if statusLabel}}
  <p class="verdict-line__eyebrow verdict-line__eyebrow--{{status}}">{{statusLabel}}</p>
  {{/if}}
  <p class="verdict-line__sentence">{{{sentence}}}</p>
  <p class="verdict-line__meta">{{meta}}</p>
</header>
